### Performance Budget (Revised)

With the expanded demo (three tabs, knowledge graph), the performance budget needs adjustment:

| Asset | Size Budget | Load Strategy |
|-------|-------------|---------------|
| Initial HTML + CSS | < 50KB | Inline critical CSS |
| Hero animation JS | < 30KB | Async, after LCP |
| Demo Tab 1 (search) | < 80KB | Lazy load on scroll proximity |
| Demo Tab 2 (graph) | < 50KB | Lazy load on tab click |
| Demo Tab 3 (share) | < 30KB | Lazy load on tab click |
| Mock data | < 40KB | Lazy load with Demo Tab 1 |
| GSAP + ScrollTrigger | < 30KB | Async |
| React Flow | < 45KB | Lazy load with Tab 2 |
| Fonts (variable, subset) | < 60KB | Preload, `font-display: swap` |
| **Total initial load** | **< 200KB** | |
| **Total all assets** | **< 500KB** | |

Target Core Web Vitals:
- LCP: < 1.5s (hero text + static fallback image)
- INP: < 80ms (all interactions measured)
- CLS: < 0.03 (no layout shift from font loading or lazy content)

