### New Metric: Demo-to-Docs Pipeline

Track the funnel: Demo interaction → Docs visit → GitHub visit → Waitlist signup. This four-step pipeline tells you whether your site is successfully converting curiosity into commitment. If demo interaction is high but docs visits are low, the developer section isn't compelling enough. If docs visits are high but GitHub stars are low, the open-source messaging isn't landing.

